                            About Us
                        

For more than 85 years, the Hertz Corporation has been a leader in our field, providing professional vehicle and equipment rental services to clients who rely on us to deliver innovative and customer-focused solutions. The secret of our success is our world-class team of employees and our commitment to providing rewarding career paths, fostering personal achievement and celebrating our collective success. Whether you are just starting your career or are an experienced manager searching for new challenges, Hertz offers a variety of exciting career opportunities.
If you're motivated, energetic and thrive in a fast-paced and ever-changing environment, we can offer you a rewarding career where no two days are alike. Our entrepreneurial culture can give you valuable industry insight and on-the-job experience in growing a business from the ground up. We welcome talented and competitive people, and will reward you with outstanding opportunities for personal and professional development. We also offer a program of flexible, customizable benefits, which include:
  
  Medical, dental, vision coverage, life insurance, long-term disability, flexible spending accounts, vacation, paid holidays, sick days, income-savings plans, U.S. savings bonds and Tuition reimbursement.

If you’re looking for a supportive work environment and an exciting future, then you should consider the diverse opportunities available at Hertz. To learn more about our team of professionals, join the Hertz Corporation Talent Network today!
What is a Talent Network?
Talent Networks enhance your job search and application process. Whether you choose to apply or just leave your information, we look forward to staying connected with you.
